    <p>Gate­way Kids Club Sto­ry­telling kicks off a month of Mid-Au­tumn Fes­ti­val sto­ries with the story of Chang Er, the god­dess of the moon. A leg­endary hero Hou Yi lived with his beau­ti­ful wife Chang Er. Af­ter a se­ries of amaz­ing feats, the Jade Em­peror re­warded him with an elixir of im­mor­tal­ity, but he could not bear to live for­ever with­out his wife.</p>
    <p>Gate­way The­atre pro­motes made-in-Sin­ga­pore works and tal­ent of all cul­tures.</p>
    <p>WHEN: To­mor­row, 11am</p>
    <p>AD­MIS­SION: Free with regis­tra­tion INFO: arts.gate­way.sg/ join-mail­ing-list</p>


